      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for a dependable ride with plenty of character! This vehicle is in fair condition and has served its previous owners well, showing the honest signs of a life spent on the road. While there are some cosmetic imperfections and typical wear, it remains a solid, functional choice for anyone looking for a reliable driver at a great value. It\u2019s a practical, honest car that\u2019s ready for its next chapter with you!",
