    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. It currently requires significant mechanical repairs to be roadworthy, as the engine runs roughly and the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping. The exterior shows substantial wear, including various dents, rusted panels, and fading paint, while the interior has several tears in the upholstery and non-functional electronics. This would be an ideal project for a dedicated restorer or could serve as a donor vehicle for parts.",
